headline: 5 Stocks to Watch From the Thriving Insurance Brokerage Industry
summary: The increased demand for insurance products, strategic acquisitions and the adoption of technology are likely to drive the performance of Zacks Insurance Brokerage industry players like ERIE, BRO, MMC, AJG and AON.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Litchfield Special Risks, Inc.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced that its U.S. wholesale brokerage, binding authority and programs division, Risk Placement Services, Inc. (RPS), has acquired El Paso, Texas-based Litchfield Special Risks, Inc. (LSR). Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
